# NTNT Language Website
# Official website for ntnt-lang.org
# Run: ntnt intent check server.tnt

## Overview
A clean, modern website introducing the NTNT programming language.
Built with NTNT's file-based routing, external templates, and middleware.

## Design
- Colors: #137EA2 (teal), #F1993F (orange), #2C2A74 (indigo), #192F52 (navy), #FCDD83 (yellow), #20DDE3 (cyan)
- Hero: Full 100vw edge-to-edge, warm premium gradient (indigo → violet → orange glow)
- Header: Dark glass effect with backdrop blur, floating over hero
- Clean, modern aesthetic with responsive design

