## Glossary

| Term | Means |
|------|-------|
| a visitor goes to the {path} | GET {path} |
| a visitor goes to {path} | GET {path} |
| home page | / |
| learn page | /learn |
| blog | /blog |
| page loads successfully | status 200, returns HTML |
| returns HTML | header "Content-Type" contains "text/html" |
| has site branding | body contains "ntnt-logo", body contains "NTNT" |
| has powered badge | body contains "Powered by NTNT", body contains "powered-badge" |
| has navigation | body contains "Learn", body contains "Blog" |
| has proper layout | has site branding, has navigation, body contains "footer" |
| they see {text} | body contains {text} |
| they don't see {text} | body not contains {text} |
| page not found | status 404 |
| blog post exists | status 200, returns HTML |
| blog post missing | body contains "Post Not Found" |

