## Components

Component: Branded Page
  id: component.branded_page
  description: "A page with consistent NTNT branding and layout"
  inherent_behavior:
    - Site logo and title visible
    - Navigation links present
    - Footer with copyright
    - Consistent styling applied

Component: Blog Post
  id: component.blog_post
  parameters:
    - slug: the URL slug for the post
    - title: the post title
  inherent_behavior:
    - Post title displayed
    - Author and date shown
    - Content rendered from template
    - Back link to blog index

